    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Chapel Hill.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Chapel Hill?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Chapel Hill property values are driven by elevated position, large block sizes, established tree canopy and Kenmore State High School catchment proximity. Families who want space and bushland character within 12 kilometres of the CBD and buyers upgrading from the density of Toowong or Indooroopilly consistently find Chapel Hill's land content and streetscape justify the price premium over neighbouring western suburbs.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Chapel Hill?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Chapel Hill homes typically sell within 30 to 50 days. The suburb draws a focused buyer pool: families prioritising school catchments and bushland character, buyers upgrading from the western corridor, and owner-occupiers who have been watching the suburb for an extended period. Competition is strongest during autumn and spring, with well-positioned homes on elevated blocks attracting the most motivated buyers.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Chapel Hill?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Chapel Hill offers a leafy, elevated western Brisbane lifestyle approximately 12 kilometres from the CBD. Generous blocks, established eucalyptus canopy and a quiet residential character shaped by decades of family owner-occupation define the suburb. Access to Kenmore Plaza and Indooroopilly Shopping Centre provides everyday retail, while the Western Freeway and Moggill Road corridors make the CBD accessible by car and by bus.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Chapel Hill a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Chapel Hill offers a combination of land size, established bushland character and school catchment quality that is genuinely scarce at its price point in the western corridor. Buyers who find Paddington or Toowong beyond their budget for detached homes on generous blocks consistently discover Chapel Hill offers comparable liveability with more space. The suburb's low turnover and stable owner-occupier base underpin long-term value.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

